Class Key

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cinchapi.concourse.db.Key
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ByteSized, java.lang.Comparable<Key>

    public final class Key
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Key>, ByteSized
    The primary identifier for a Row. Each key is an unsigned long, which means that the total pool of identifiers is between 0 and 2^64 - 1 inclusive.
